(1, 1, '2026-03-02', '{\"salary_monthly\": 50000.0, \"total_spent_today\": 1200.5, \"total_spent_this_month\": 18350.75, \"balance_this_month\": 31649.25, \"expenses_today\": [{\"id\": \"1719972000001\", \"date\": \"2026-03-02\", \"amount\": 250.0, \"note\": \"Breakfast\"}, {\"id\": \"1719972000002\", \"date\": \"2026-03-02\", \"amount\": 950.5, \"note\": \"Groceries\"}], \"all_expenses\": [{\"id\": \"1719800000001\", \"date\": \"2026-03-01\", \"amount\": 1000.0, \"note\": \"Rent\"}]}', 'You\'re on track with spending this month. Set aside a fixed amount right after payday for savings to avoid overspending.', '2026-03-02 08:59:42'),
(2, 1, '2025-02-26', '{\"salary_monthly\": 40000.0, \"total_spent_today\": 0.0, \"total_spent_this_month\": 0.0, \"balance_this_month\": 40000.0, \"expenses_today\": [], \"recent_transactions\": []}', NULL, '2026-03-02 09:08:00'),
(3, 4, '2026-03-02', '{\"salary_monthly\": 30000.0, \"total_spent_today\": 500.0, \"total_spent_this_month\": 500.0, \"balance_this_month\": 29500.0, \"expenses_today\": [{\"id\": \"1772422247777\", \"date\": \"2026-03-02\", \"amount\": 500.0, \"note\": \"groceries\"}], \"recent_transactions\": [{\"id\": \"1772078660469\", \"date\": \"2026-02-26\", \"amount\": 300.0, \"note\": \"food\"}, {\"id\": \"1772422247777\", \"date\": \"2026-03-02\", \"amount\": 500.0, \"note\": \"groceries\"}]}', 'Hey there! Great start to the month keeping track of your spending.\n\nTo make your 30000 salary work best, try setting a clear budget for different categories like \'Needs,\' \'Wants,\' and \'Savings\' right at the beginning of the month. Consider automating a transfer of at least 3000, or 10% of your salary, into a dedicated savings account on payday to grow your funds effortlessly. Make it a habit to quickly review your spending balance in UniMind every few days to stay mindful of your financial goals.', '2026-03-02 09:14:35'),
(4, 4, '2026-03-02', '{\"salary_monthly\": 30000.0, \"total_spent_today\": 500.0, \"total_spent_this_month\": 500.0, \"balance_this_month\": 29500.0, \"expenses_today\": [{\"id\": \"1772422247777\", \"date\": \"2026-03-02\", \"amount\": 500.0, \"note\": \"groceries\"}], \"recent_transactions\": [{\"id\": \"1772078660469\", \"date\": \"2026-02-26\", \"amount\": 300.0, \"note\": \"food\"}, {\"id\": \"1772422247777\", \"date\": \"2026-03-02\", \"amount\": 500.0, \"note\": \"groceries\"}]}', 'Hey there! Great job tracking your spending so early in the month. Here are a few tips to keep you on a strong financial path:\n\nConsider setting up an automatic transfer for a portion of your 30000 salary, like 10-20%, into a separate savings account right at the start of each month.\nUse the UniMind app to create a simple budget for your 30000 salary, clearly separating funds for essentials and fun.\nTake a moment to categorize your 500 spending today within the UniMind app to better understand your habits.', '2026-03-02 09:14:35'),
(5, 1, '2025-02-26', '{\"salary_monthly\": 40000.0, \"total_spent_today\": 0.0, \"total_spent_this_month\": 0.0, \"balance_this_month\": 40000.0, \"expenses_today\": [], \"recent_transactions\": []}', NULL, '2026-03-02 09:14:58'),
(6, 4, '2026-03-02', '{\"salary_monthly\": 30000.0, \"total_spent_today\": 500.0, \"total_spent_this_month\": 500.0, \"balance_this_month\": 29500.0, \"expenses_today\": [{\"id\": \"1772422247777\", \"date\": \"2026-03-02\", \"amount\": 500.0, \"note\": \"groceries\"}], \"recent_transactions\": [{\"id\": \"1772078660469\", \"date\": \"2026-02-26\", \"amount\": 300.0, \"note\": \"food\"}, {\"id\": \"1772422247777\", \"date\": \"2026-03-02\", \"amount\": 500.0, \"note\": \"groceries\"}]}', 'Great start to the month! With your 30000 salary, let\'s set you up for success.\n\nMap out your 30000 monthly salary into categories like \'needs,\' \'wants,\' and \'savings\' right at the start of the month.\nSet up an automatic transfer of at least 20% of your 30000 salary, or 6000, to a dedicated savings account on payday.\nFor every future purchase, take a brief moment to ask yourself if it\'s a \'need\' or a \'want\' to encourage mindful spending.', '2026-03-02 09:35:22'),
(7, 4, '2026-03-02', '{\"salary_monthly\": 30000.0, \"total_spent_today\": 500.0, \"total_spent_this_month\": 500.0, \"balance_this_month\": 29500.0, \"expenses_today\": [{\"id\": \"1772422247777\", \"date\": \"2026-03-02\", \"amount\": 500.0, \"note\": \"groceries\"}], \"recent_transactions\": [{\"id\": \"1772078660469\", \"date\": \"2026-02-26\", \"amount\": 300.0, \"note\": \"food\"}, {\"id\": \"1772422247777\", \"date\": \"2026-03-02\", \"amount\": 500.0, \"note\": \"groceries\"}]}', 'Error: You exceeded your current quota, please check your plan and billing details. For more information on this error, head to: https://ai.google.dev/gemini-api/docs/rate-limits. To monitor your current usage, head to: https://ai.dev/rate-limit. \n* Quota exceeded for metric: generativelanguage.googleapis.com/generate_content_free_tier_requests, limit: 20, model: gemini-2.5-flash\nPlease retry in 29.240101445s.', '2026-03-02 09:40:31'),
(8, 4, '2026-03-02', '{\"salary_monthly\": 30000.0, \"total_spent_today\": 500.0, \"total_spent_this_month\": 500.0, \"balance_this_month\": 29500.0, \"expenses_today\": [{\"id\": \"1772422247777\", \"date\": \"2026-03-02\", \"amount\": 500.0, \"note\": \"groceries\"}], \"recent_transactions\": [{\"id\": \"1772078660469\", \"date\": \"2026-02-26\", \"amount\": 300.0, \"note\": \"food\"}, {\"id\": \"1772422247777\", \"date\": \"2026-03-02\", \"amount\": 500.0, \"note\": \"groceries\"}]}', 'Welcome back! With a salary of 30000.0, you have a great foundation for financial success.\n\nConsider setting up a simple monthly budget today, like the 50/30/20 rule, to guide your spending for the rest of the month.\nAutomate a transfer of at least 10% of your salary to a separate savings account on payday to build your savings effortlessly.\nBefore your next purchase, take a quick moment to consider if it aligns with your monthly financial goals to make conscious spending choices.', '2026-03-02 09:40:35'),
(9, 4, '2026-03-02', '{\"salary_monthly\": 30000.0, \"total_spent_today\": 1500.0, \"total_spent_this_month\": 1500.0, \"balance_this_month\": 28500.0, \"expenses_today\": [{\"id\": \"1772422247777\", \"date\": \"2026-03-02\", \"amount\": 500.0, \"note\": \"groceries\"}, {\"id\": \"1772424650369\", \"date\": \"2026-03-02\", \"amount\": 1000.0, \"note\": \"cricket bat\"}], \"recent_transactions\": [{\"id\": \"1772078660469\", \"date\": \"2026-02-26\", \"amount\": 300.0, \"note\": \"food\"}, {\"id\": \"1772422247777\", \"date\": \"2026-03-02\", \"amount\": 500.0, \"note\": \"groceries\"}, {\"id\": \"1772424650369\", \"date\": \"2026-03-02\", \"amount\": 1000.0, \"note\": \"cricket bat\"}]}', NULL, '2026-03-02 09:40:50'),
