(12, 4, '2026-03-02', '{\"salary_monthly\": 30000.0, \"total_spent_today\": 1500.0, \"total_spent_this_month\": 1500.0, \"balance_this_month\": 28500.0, \"expenses_today\": [{\"id\": \"1772422247777\", \"date\": \"2026-03-02\", \"amount\": 500.0, \"note\": \"groceries\"}, {\"id\": \"1772424650369\", \"date\": \"2026-03-02\", \"amount\": 1000.0, \"note\": \"cricket bat\"}], \"recent_transactions\": [{\"id\": \"1772078660469\", \"date\": \"2026-02-26\", \"amount\": 300.0, \"note\": \"food\"}, {\"id\": \"1772422247777\", \"date\": \"2026-03-02\", \"amount\": 500.0, \"note\": \"groceries\"}, {\"id\": \"1772424650369\", \"date\": \"2026-03-02\", \"amount\": 1000.0, \"note\": \"cricket bat\"}]}', 'Hi there!\n\nStart by reflecting on today\'s 1500 expenditure to understand if it aligns with your financial priorities. Take the opportunity early in the month to create a budget for your 30000 salary, assigning specific amounts to different spending categories. Automate a transfer of a portion of your salary to a dedicated savings account right after payday to build your savings effortlessly.', '2026-03-02 09:42:05'),
