(125, 5, '2026-03-10', '{\"salary_monthly\": 65000.0, \"total_spent_today\": 0.0, \"total_spent_this_month\": 2600.0, \"balance_this_month\": 62400.0, \"expenses_today\": [], \"recent_transactions\": [{\"id\": \"1773048000842\", \"date\": \"2026-03-09\", \"amount\": 2500.0, \"note\": \"groceries\"}, {\"id\": \"1773048447019\", \"date\": \"2026-03-09\", \"amount\": 100.0, \"note\": \"food\"}]}', 'Before your next payday, outline a simple budget, allocating portions of your 65000 to essentials, savings, and wants.\nAutomate a transfer to move a specific amount from your salary into savings right after you get paid, making saving effortless.\nRegularly check your spending against your plan throughout the month to stay mindful and make informed financial choices.', '2026-03-10 19:50:35'),
